- ⚠️ Sharing within organizations (requires confirmation)
- ❌ Commercial use (explicit permission required)
- ❌ Public redistribution without proper attribution

For permissions, please contact:
- Amazon Web Services: https://aws.amazon.com/contact-us/
- Original author: Raju SP

